data.name: xrTableCell54.Text
data.value: When tested in accordance with 8.1 - A single lens goggle that allows the missile to rupture the lens shall constitute a failure. 單片式雪鏡鏡片若遭椎體破壞，就算失敗。 - A single lens goggle that allows the frame or lens to fracture shall constitute a failure.單片式雪鏡框或片若有破裂，就算失敗。 - A thermal (dual) lens goggle that allows the missile to penetrate or fracture the inner lens shall constitute a failure. 雙層片雪鏡若內片遭椎體穿透或破裂， 就算失敗。 - Any displacement or dislodgment of any lens by more than 25% in single or thermal (dual) lens goggles from its original position within the frame constitutes a failure. 雪鏡鏡片若有超過 25% 面積剝落，算失敗。

data.name: xrTableCell35.Text
data.value: Mechanical Requirements: 5 2 3 機械性要求(尖錐測試)

data.name: xrTableCell36.Text
data.value: Tested in accordance with 8.1, - any displaed fragments, separated delaminations, or complete fracture of the frame or lenses constitute a failure. - No contact with the eye of the head form shall be permitted either by the lens of the protector or the projectile itself. Note: A protector that is dislodged from the test headform shall not constitute a failure provided all of the above mechanical requirements are met.按照 8.1 測試 500 克重 High Mass 尖錐 127 cm 高處自由墜落衝擊護具測試以後，不可有任何表面碎片剝落、脫離、破裂 (龜裂)、組件分開、鏡片穿透 (或者離開原來組裝所在位置)。鏡片內側不可碰觸到人頭眼球。
